---
import { CldImage } from 'astro-cloudinary';
import LADExperiment from '../features/LADExperiment.astro';
---

<!-- LAD Experiment Section -->
<section class='relative py-20 lg:py-32' id='lad-section'>
  <!-- Background Glow -->
  <!-- Background Glow (hidden on mobile to prevent hard edges from overflow clipping) -->
  <div
    class='hidden md:block absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[radial-gradient(circle,var(--color-purple-500)_0%,transparent_70%)] opacity-10 rounded-full translate-x-1/2 pointer-events-none'
  >
  </div>

  <div class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 page-container relative z-10'>
    <!-- 1. The Hook: 30-Second Test -->
    <div class='text-center max-w-192 mx-auto mb-16'>
      <div
        class='inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm font-medium text-white mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm'
      >
        <span class='animate-pulse text-yellow-400'>â±ï¸</span>
        <span>Tes 30 Detik</span>
      </div>

      <h2
        class='text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight text-balance'
      >
        Buktikan Sendiri dalam 30 Detik: Kamu Punya <span
          class='text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-400'
          >"Insting Bahasa"</span
        > yang Kuat Banget.
      </h2>
      <p
        class='text-base sm:text-lg text-(--token-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-pretty'
      >
        Jangan cuma percaya omongan kami. Yuk, kita buktiin bareng-bareng
        sekarang jugaâ€”cuma butuh 30 detik doang. Kami yakin kamu bakal langsung
        ngerasain "wah, bener juga" sendiri.
        <br /><br />
        Baca dua kalimat Bahasa Indonesia ini pelan-pelan:
      </p>
    </div>

    <LADExperiment />

    <!-- 3. Immediate Reaction Text -->
    <div
      class='w-full mx-auto text-center mb-24 hidden lad-reaction opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-700'
      style='max-width: 48rem;'
    >
      <p class='text-xl lg:text-2xl text-white font-medium leading-relaxed'>
        <span class='text-emerald-400'>"Wah, bener juga."</span><br />
        Tanpa buka buku tata bahasa, tanpa mikir S-P-O-K atau aturan apa pun... kamu
        langsung ngerasa kalimat nomor 2 itu aneh banget, kan?
      </p>
      <div class='w-full mx-auto mt-4' style='max-width: 42rem;'>
        <p class='text-lg text-(--token-text-secondary)'>
          Rasanya "nggak enak" dibaca, kayak ada yang salah, meskipun kamu masih
          bisa nangkep maksudnya secara kasar (lupa dompet pas mau beli
          takoyaki).
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 4. The Deep Dive (Grid) -->
    <div class='grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-20 items-center mb-24'>
      <div class='lg:col-span-5 order-2 lg:order-1 hidden lg:block'>
        <div class='skeuo-card p-4 lg:p-6'>
          <div
            class='relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-inner border border-white/10 group'
          >
            <CldImage
              src='LAD_Generated_Image_16yr3x16yr3x16yr_ygwtpf'
              alt='Visualisasi Language Acquisition Device (LAD)'
              width={1000}
              height={1000}
              crop='fill'
              class='w-full h-auto transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-in-out'
            />
            <div
              class='absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/80 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-60'
            >
            </div>
            <div class='absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6'>
              <div
                class='text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-white/70 uppercase mb-1 skeuo-text-emboss'
              >
                Konsep
              </div>
              <div class='text-lg font-bold text-white skeuo-text-emboss'>
                The Language Acquisition Device
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='lg:col-span-7 order-1 lg:order-2 space-y-8'>
        <div class='skeuo-card overflow-hidden p-6 md:p-8 relative'>
          <!-- Purple Ambient Spotlight -->
          <div
            class='absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,oklch(0.586_0.246_293/0.15)_0%,transparent_70%)] pointer-events-none'
          >
          </div>
          <h3 class='text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 skeuo-text-emboss'>
            Kenapa kamu langsung tahu itu salah dan terasa janggal? ğŸ¤”
          </h3>
          <div
            class='space-y-6 text-lg text-(--token-text-secondary) leading-relaxed'
          >
            <p>
              Bukan karena kamu hafal rumus grammar Indonesia dari SD. Kamu tahu
              karena kamu punya <strong class='text-purple-400'
                >insting bahasa alami</strong
              > yang disebut <span class='text-white'
                >Language Acquisition Device (LAD)</span
              > oleh Prof. Chomskyâ€”semacam "perangkat bawaan" di otak manusia yang
              aktif sejak lahir untuk menyerap bahasa secara intuitif lewat paparan
              terus-menerus.
            </p>

            <!-- Mobile-only LAD Image -->
            <div class='lg:hidden my-6'>
              <div class='skeuo-card p-3'>
                <div
                  class='relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-inner border border-white/10'
                >
                  <CldImage
                    src='LAD_Generated_Image_16yr3x16yr3x16yr_ygwtpf'
                    alt='Visualisasi Language Acquisition Device (LAD)'
                    width={800}
                    height={800}
                    crop='fill'
                    class='w-full h-auto'
                  />
                  <div
                    class='absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/80 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-60'
                  >
                  </div>
                  <div class='absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4'>
                    <div
                      class='text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-white/70 uppercase mb-1 skeuo-text-emboss'
                    >
                      Konsep
                    </div>
                    <div
                      class='text-base font-bold text-white skeuo-text-emboss'
                    >
                      The Language Acquisition Device
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p>
              LAD ini yang bikin kamu otomatis "merasa" mana kalimat yang
              natural dan mana yang pincang, tanpa perlu analisa rumus.
            </p>
            <div
              class='skeuo-inset p-6 my-6 shadow-[inset_0_2px_4px_oklch(0_0_0/0.6),0_1px_1px_oklch(1_0_0/0.05)]'
            >
              <p
                class='text-base text-(--token-text-secondary) leading-relaxed italic'
              >
                "Kalimat nomor 2 itu sengaja kami bikin mirip kayak terjemahan
                mentah-mentah dari orang Jepang yang lagi belajar Bahasa
                Indonesiaâ€”mereka nerjemahin kata per kata sesuai struktur
                Jepang, jadi urutannya campur aduk, partikelnya ngawur..."
              </p>
            </div>
            <p>
              Kamu masih bisa paham maksudnya (karena konteksnya jelas), tapi
              rasanya "off" banget, unsettling, kayak denger orang ngomong tapi
              agak pincang.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 5. The Conclusion / Bridge -->
    <div class='max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-12'>
      <!-- Success Box -->
      <div
        class='skeuo-card p-8 lg:p-10 relative overflow-hidden bg-[oklch(0.17_0.04_286)]! border-indigo-400/30!'
      >
        <div
          class='absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-full blur-[80px] pointer-events-none'
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class='relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 items-center'
        >
          <div
            class='shrink-0 p-4 skeuo-inset rounded-full shadow-[inset_0_2px_4px_oklch(0_0_0/0.6),0_1px_1px_oklch(1_0_0/0.1)] text-4xl border border-indigo-500/30'
          >
            ğŸŒ±
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4
              class='text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 skeuo-text-emboss'
            >
              Selamat! Kamu baru saja buktiin sendiri.
            </h4>
            <p class='text-lg text-(--token-text-secondary) leading-relaxed'>
              LAD di otakmu masih aktif dan super kuat. Perangkat bawaan itu
              udah jalan lancar buat Bahasa Indonesia sejak kamu kecil.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- The Problem & Solution -->
      <div class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8'>
        <!-- Problem Card -->
        <div
          class='p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl bg-linear-to-br from-red-500/10 to-transparent border border-red-500/20 space-y-4 shadow-lg'
        >
          <h4
            class='text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-red-400 flex items-start gap-3'
          >
            <div class='mt-1 shrink-0'>
              <svg
                xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
                width='20'
                height='20'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                fill='none'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                stroke-linecap='round'
                stroke-linejoin='round'
                class='lucide lucide-x-circle'
                ><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='10'></circle><path d='m15 9-6 6'
                ></path><path d='m9 9 6 6'></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <span>Masalahnya di bahasa Jepang?</span>
          </h4>
          <div
            class='space-y-3 text-[15px] sm:text-base text-white/80 leading-relaxed text-pretty'
          >
            <p>
              Metode tradisional (hafal bunpou dulu, terjemahin dulu) justru <strong
                class='text-white'>mematikan LAD itu</strong
              > sebelum dia sempat bekerja optimal.
            </p>
            <p>
              Mereka paksa kamu mikir lewat rumus (surface structure), bukan
              lewat insting alami (deep structure).
            </p>
            <p>
              Akibatnya, intuisi nativemu buat Jepang nggak pernah
              terbentukâ€”kamu jadi <span class='text-red-300'
                >gagap, loading lama, dan keluarnya kaku</span
              >.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Solution Card -->
        <div
          class='p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl bg-linear-to-br from-emerald-500/10 to-transparent border border-emerald-500/20 space-y-4 shadow-lg'
        >
          <h4
            class='text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-emerald-400 flex items-start gap-3'
          >
            <div class='mt-1 shrink-0'>
              <svg
                xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
                width='20'
                height='20'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                fill='none'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                stroke-linecap='round'
                stroke-linejoin='round'
                class='lucide lucide-check-circle'
                ><path d='M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14'></path><polyline
                  points='22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01'></polyline></svg
              >
            </div>
            <span>Metode Solusi & Komunitas Immersion</span>
          </h4>
          <div
            class='space-y-3 text-[15px] sm:text-base text-white/80 leading-relaxed text-pretty'
          >
            <p>
              Kami cuma mengaktifkan kembali LAD yang samaâ€”yang udah terbukti
              works di Bahasa Indonesia kamuâ€”buat bahasa Jepang.
            </p>
            <p>
              Caranya? Dengan kasih <strong class='text-emerald-300'
                >comprehensible input</strong
              > yang pas, sampai LAD-mu bangun intuisi nativenya sendiri secara alami
              tanpa perlu dihafal.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
